{"tid":1779602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[爆料] 鄭經翰指湯家驊2004年曾透露被掌黑材料　湯否認兼指遭抺黑","createTime":"2019-12-11T19:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T16:11:57.000Z","uid":297241,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"14f61be9254704979b7c301937752532f6d031b6","tid":1779602,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T19:28:03.000Z","msg":"鄭經翰指湯家驊2004年曾透露被掌黑材料　<br />\n湯否認兼指遭抺黑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正當特首林鄭月娥因逃犯條例而弄得焦頭爛額、內閣行政會議成員均遭拖累之際，前電台名咀、「大班」鄭經翰上周六（15日）罕有地在網台節目聲稱，行會成員<span style=\"color: red;\">湯家驊2004年曾於聚會上自稱被傳媒掌握黑材料</span>，不清楚湯是否因此轉投建制陣營。<br />\n<br />\n上述視頻近日在網上廣泛流傳。《香港01》今午（18日）向湯家驊查詢鄭經翰所言是否屬實，<span style=\"color: red;\">湯強烈否認自己被人掌握黑材料</span>，而「聚會」等私人場合便不置評論。湯又批評，有關言論抹黑他，是對他的攻擊。"},{"pid":"cb692e8889993f70e6d0ff67f1085e191ccc8a6d","tid":1779602,"uid":26770,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T19:32:52.000Z","msg":"衰十一斷正，淚灑雪廠街，閃卡藏西環，一生為共奴"},{"pid":"3826be941e96e46c512ca42de05766db324ccb33","tid":1779602,"uid":205013,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T19:33:52.000Z","msg":"十一大狀有名你叫，差在係咪插入性性侵"},{"pid":"46e15ec3fca0e5ab79a31f223fbd286374c6fb47","tid":1779602,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"呢排佢去左邊?"},{"pid":"e222f52528c86f00d204bdd58651529bd84ad958","tid":1779602,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T19:43:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"81ad612064341755b7c6f4de29626d73c5545086","tid":1779602,"uid":294221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T20:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYhwT7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYhwT7Z.jpg&h=8f219d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人嘅最強後盾</span></span><br />